00:02:48.690 --> 00:02:52.290
to honor Judy and Gwen's
groundbreaking accomplishments,

00:02:52.290 --> 00:02:55.440
both as a team and
as individuals.

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:57.210
It will include a
panel discussion

00:02:57.210 --> 00:03:00.150
to probe the challenges
facing journalism today.

00:03:00.150 --> 00:03:02.079
Please visit the
Radcliffe website

00:03:02.079 --> 00:03:03.870
for more information
on the day and how you

00:03:03.870 --> 00:03:06.510
